headline: Dow Jones Futures: Nvidia Earnings Are Next Test After Powell-Led Stock Market Rally
summary: Fed chief Powell's dovish speech triggered a big Friday rally, with the S&P 500 and Dow Jones hitting new highs and several stocks flashing buy signals. Nvidia earnings loom.

headline: Uber Leads 5 Stocks Near Buy Points As Market Rebounds
summary: Uber, JPMorgan and RTX are stocks to watch. The market jumped Friday as Fed chief Powell hinted at rate cuts.

headline: JPMorgan (JPM) and MUFG Eye $22B Loan for Texas AI-Driven Data Hub
summary: JPMorgan Chase & Co. (NYSE:JPM) is one of the best stocks to buy according to billionaire Ken Fisher. On August 20, JPMorgan Chase and Mitsubishi UFJ Financial Group entered talks to underwrite a $22 billion loan for a major data center project in Texas, led by Vantage Data Centers, backed by Silver Lake and DigitalBridge.
